high_descs: Move forward then take left and head toward the end then take right move to the bed to your left.
Take the saltshaker from the bed.
Turn right and move forward to the desklamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine the SaltShaker on the DeskLamp.

high_descs: Turn left and walk down the hallway then go into the last room on the right and face the bed.
Pick up the saltshaker from the bed.
Turn right to face the desklamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine the SaltShaker under the light of the DeskLamp.

high_descs: Go straight and left towards the corridor, walk into the corridor, enter the right side last room, then turn left, look at the bed.
Take the saltshaker from the bed.
anns.task_desc: To get the SaltShaker from the bedroom and switch on the DeskLamp.
